<td><div style="float:left;margin-right:1em"><span typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:Vineyard_at_Wyken_Hall_-_geograph.org.uk_-_216836.jpg" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/99/Vineyard_at_Wyken_Hall_-_geograph.org.uk_-_216836.jpg/200px-Vineyard_at_Wyken_Hall_-_geograph.org.uk_-_216836.jpg" decoding="async" width="200" height="133" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/99/Vineyard_at_Wyken_Hall_-_geograph.org.uk_-_216836.jpg/300px-Vineyard_at_Wyken_Hall_-_geograph.org.uk_-_216836.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/99/Vineyard_at_Wyken_Hall_-_geograph.org.uk_-_216836.jpg/400px-Vineyard_at_Wyken_Hall_-_geograph.org.uk_-_216836.jpg 2x" data-file-width="640" data-file-height="427" /></a></span>
</div>
</td>
<td align="center">... that <a href="/wiki/Global_warming" class="mw-redirect" title="Global warming">global warming</a> is cited as the main reason why southern <a href="/wiki/England" title="England">England</a> is becoming <i>suitable</i> for <b><a href="/wiki/Wine_from_the_United_Kingdom" title="Wine from the United Kingdom">wine production</a></b> and that it has similar soils and latitude to the Champagne region of <a href="/wiki/France" title="France">France</a>?<br />
<p>(<i>Pictured left: A vineyard in <a href="/wiki/Wyken" title="Wyken">Wyken</a>, a suburb of <a href="/wiki/Coventry" title="Coventry">Coventry</a>, England</i>)
</p>
