<ul><li><a href="/wiki/Albedo" title="Albedo">Albedo</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Carbon_cycle" title="Carbon cycle">Carbon cycle</a>
<ul><li><a href="/wiki/Atmospheric_carbon_cycle" title="Atmospheric carbon cycle">atmospheric</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Biological_pump" title="Biological pump">biologic</a></li>
